        "subject": "LU-1415 tests: Handling of ZFS's delayed space updates",
        "message": "LU-1415 tests: Handling of ZFS's delayed space updates\n\nSpace-related updates, such as changes of dn_used and of ds_used_bytes,\nare invisible to opertions like dt_attr_get() and dt_statfs() until\nafter corresponding transaction groups start to be synchronized.  This\npatch makes sure the tests do a dt_sync() for each OST before checking\nspace usage.\n\nChange-Id: I33a86d984e70a88c87300e705dd200462432770c\nSigned-off-by: Li Wei <liwei@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
